<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1004786' id='t-1004786'>I say, there's only a few materials
that you should completely avoid.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007831' id='t-1007831'>The rest of them, it's all about application,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1009730' id='t-1009730'>and at the end of the day, everything
