<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1012749' id='t-1012749'>or buy as consumers is done so for function.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1015089' id='t-1015089'>We want something, therefore we buy it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1017206' id='t-1017206'>So breaking things back down and delivering</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1020362' id='t-1020362'>smartly, elegantly, sophisticated solutions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1024361' id='t-1024361'>that take into consideration the entire system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1027158' id='t-1027158'>and the entire life of the thing, everything,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1030253' id='t-1030253'>all the way back to the extraction
