</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1035891' id='t-1035891'>And I'll just leave you with one very quick thing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1037961' id='t-1037961'>that a designer said to me recently 
