<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1048928' id='t-1048928'>and turned and he said to me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1050869' id='t-1050869'>'I know it's going to cost less,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1052634' id='t-1052634'>I know it's going to sell more,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1054252' id='t-1054252'>but we're not pioneers, because
