</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1058725' id='t-1058725'>I think we've got a roomful of pioneers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1060942' id='t-1060942'>and I hope there are far more pioneers out there,
