</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1064027' id='t-1064027'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:56
